 //╷         ╷       ╷       ╷       ╷       ╷              ╷         ╷╷         ╷         ╷                 ╷       ╷                ╷         ╷         ╷
              &trans  &kp N7  &kp N8  &kp N9  &kp MINUS                           &trans    &rgb_ug RGB_EFF   &kp UP  &rgb_ug RGB_BRI  &trans         
